@node MAIN "Welcome"

BladeEnc Manual
---------------

BladeEnc
Blade's MP3 Encoder
version 0.82
Release Date: July 22, 1999
written by Tord Jansson,
based on sourcecode from ISO
E-mail: @{b}tord.jansson@swipnet.se@{ub}
Homepage: @{b}http://bladeenc.cjb.net@{ub}

This manual is written for the Windows version of BladeEnc.
Various ports may differ slightly in some aspects (but normally
they don't).

